    How to Migrate from create-react-app to Vite using Jest and Browserslist
    The React team no longer recommends using create-react-app (CRA) [https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app] as a bundler to create a new React application. The team and community realized that even though CRA was a jump-starter, it lacked the flexibility needed to configure or manage large and complex applications. Nowadays, the team recommends using production-grade  ( 8 min )
